Package: drumkit
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Low-latency TUI MIDI drum sampler for electronic drum kits
 drumkit is a terminal-based MIDI drum sampler that provides low-latency
 audio playback for electronic drum kits. It supports MIDI input mapping,
 multiple audio sample formats, and a ratatui-based terminal UI.
